# Decision Support Engine

See [DECISION_SUPPORT_ENGINE.md](../../DECISION_SUPPORT_ENGINE.md).

## Rules

1. Business-first — support prioritization and operational insights before personal guidance.
2. Aipify advises; users decide. Never auto-execute or dictate outcomes.
3. Every recommendation includes reasoning, confidence (low/moderate/high), and optional trade-offs.
4. Business logic in Supabase RPCs; panels and API routes are thin clients.
5. Chat guidance via `detectDecisionIntent()` — no confirmation flow; link to `/app/assistant/decisions`.
6. User controls: domains, proactivity, personal support, historical data, presentation style.
7. Platform uses `get_platform_decisions_overview` — aggregates only.
8. i18n: `customerApp.decisionSupport.*`, `platform.decisionSupport.*` in en/no/sv/da.

## Tables

`dse_settings` · `decision_recommendations` · `decision_history`

## Route

`/app/assistant/decisions`
